==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Substantially
<hw>Sub*stan"tial*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a substantial manner;
in substance; essentially.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In him all his Father shone,⟦br⟧
<qex>Substantially</qex> expressed.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The laws of this religion would make men, if they would truly
observe them, <qex>substantially</qex> religious toward God, chastle,
and temperate.</q> <rj><qau>Tillotson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Substantialness</ent>⟦br⟧
